{
  "video_id": "85hbMtegrLc",
  "title": "What comes after tragedy? Forgiveness | Azim Khamisa and Ples Felix",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13600.0,
      "end_time": 17976.0,
      "text": "Azim Khamisa: We humans have many defining moments in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18000.0,
      "end_time": 20200.0,
      "text": "Sometimes these moments are joyous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20840.0,
      "end_time": 23216.0,
      "text": "and sometimes they are heartbreaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23240.0,
      "end_time": 24599.0,
      "text": "tragic."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25240.0,
      "end_time": 30200.0,
      "text": "But at these defining moments, if we are able to make the right choice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30920.0,
      "end_time": 33856.0,
      "text": "we literally manifest a miracle"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33880.0,
      "end_time": 36520.0,
      "text": "in us and others."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37480.0,
      "end_time": 39895.0,
      "text": "My only son Tariq, a university student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39920.0,
      "end_time": 44375.0,
      "text": "kind, generous, a good writer, a good photographer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44400.0,
      "end_time": 47815.0,
      "text": "had aspirations to work for National Geographic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47840.0,
      "end_time": 49896.0,
      "text": "engaged to a beautiful lady,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49920.0,
      "end_time": 53560.0,
      "text": "worked as a pizza deliveryman on Fridays and Saturdays."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54320.0,
      "end_time": 56576.0,
      "text": "He was lured to a bogus address"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56600.0,
      "end_time": 57800.0,
      "text": "by a youth gang."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 59160.0,
      "end_time": 61120.0,
      "text": "And in a gang initiation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61880.0,
      "end_time": 65440.0,
      "text": "a 14-year-old shot and killed him."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66960.0,
      "end_time": 70295.0,
      "text": "The sudden, senseless death"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70320.0,
      "end_time": 74520.0,
      "text": "of an innocent, unarmed human being;"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75720.0,
      "end_time": 77960.0,
      "text": "the overwhelming grief of a family;"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78760.0,
      "end_time": 85400.0,
      "text": "the total confusion as you try to absorb a new, hideous reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 85960.0,
      "end_time": 88976.0,
      "text": "Needless to say it brought my life to a crashing halt."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 89000.0,
      "end_time": 91456.0,
      "text": "One of the hardest things I&#39;ve ever had to do"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 91480.0,
      "end_time": 94696.0,
      "text": "was to call his mother, who lived in a different city."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 94720.0,
      "end_time": 97776.0,
      "text": "How do you tell a mother she&#39;s never going to see her son again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 97800.0,
      "end_time": 99256.0,
      "text": "or hear him laugh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 99280.0,
      "end_time": 100480.0,
      "text": "or give him a hug?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102520.0,
      "end_time": 104496.0,
      "text": "I practice as a Sufi Muslim."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104520.0,
      "end_time": 106800.0,
      "text": "I meditate two hours a day."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 107680.0,
      "end_time": 108936.0,
      "text": "And sometimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108960.0,
      "end_time": 112216.0,
      "text": "in deep trauma and deep tragedy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 112240.0,
      "end_time": 114119.0,
      "text": "there is a spark of clarity."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 115160.0,
      "end_time": 118150.0,
      "text": "So what I downloaded in my meditation"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 118400.0,
      "end_time": 121200.0,
      "text": "is that there were victims at both ends of the gun."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122400.0,
      "end_time": 126256.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easy to see that my son was a victim of the 14-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 126280.0,
      "end_time": 132160.0,
      "text": "a little bit complicated to see that he was a victim of American society."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 135495.0,
      "text": "And that begs the question, well, who is American society?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 136776.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s you and me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136800.0,
      "end_time": 140735.0,
      "text": "because I don&#39;t believe that society is just happenstance."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 140759.0,
      "end_time": 144720.0,
      "text": "I think we are all responsible for the society we&#39;ve created."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 145560.0,
      "end_time": 149360.0,
      "text": "And children killing children is not a mark of a civil society."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 150120.0,
      "end_time": 152200.0,
      "text": "So nine months after Tariq died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153400.0,
      "end_time": 155239.0,
      "text": "I started the Tariq Khamisa Foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 155840.0,
      "end_time": 158496.0,
      "text": "and our mandate at the Tariq Khamisa Foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158520.0,
      "end_time": 160976.0,
      "text": "is to stop kids from killing kids"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 161000.0,
      "end_time": 163776.0,
      "text": "by breaking the cycle of youth violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 163800.0,
      "end_time": 165696.0,
      "text": "And essentially we have three mandates."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165720.0,
      "end_time": 169520.0,
      "text": "Our first and foremost is to save lives of children."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170200.0,
      "end_time": 173799.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s important to do. We lose so many on a daily basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 174600.0,
      "end_time": 176200.0,
      "text": "Our second mandate"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 177280.0,
      "end_time": 181576.0,
      "text": "is to empower the right choices so kids don&#39;t fall through the cracks"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 181600.0,
      "end_time": 185640.0,
      "text": "and choose lives of gangs and crime and drugs and alcohol and weapons."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 186360.0,
      "end_time": 192200.0,
      "text": "And our third mandate is to teach the principles of nonviolence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 193160.0,
      "end_time": 195335.0,
      "text": "of empathy, of compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 195360.0,
      "end_time": 196760.0,
      "text": "of forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 197760.0,
      "end_time": 199696.0,
      "text": "And I started with a very simple premise"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 199720.0,
      "end_time": 201936.0,
      "text": "that violence is a learned behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 201960.0,
      "end_time": 203880.0,
      "text": "No child was born violent."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204720.0,
      "end_time": 207960.0,
      "text": "If you accept that as a truism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 207120.0,
      "end_time": 210256.0,
      "text": "nonviolence can also be a learned behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 210280.0,
      "end_time": 211616.0,
      "text": "but you have to teach it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 211640.0,
      "end_time": 213976.0,
      "text": "because kids are not going to learn that"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 214000.0,
      "end_time": 215280.0,
      "text": "through osmosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216200.0,
      "end_time": 219799.0,
      "text": "Soon after that, I reached out to my brother here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 221120.0,
      "end_time": 223296.0,
      "text": "with the attitude that we had both lost a son."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 223320.0,
      "end_time": 224576.0,
      "text": "My son died."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224600.0,
      "end_time": 226840.0,
      "text": "He lost his grandson to the adult prison system."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 227400.0,
      "end_time": 228736.0,
      "text": "And I asked him to join me."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 228760.0,
      "end_time": 233136.0,
      "text": "As you see, 22 years later, we are still here together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 233160.0,
      "end_time": 235936.0,
      "text": "because I can&#39;t bring Tariq back from the dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 235960.0,
      "end_time": 238160.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t take Tony out of prison,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 238400.0,
      "end_time": 240160.0,
      "text": "but the one thing we can do"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 240400.0,
      "end_time": 243960.0,
      "text": "is make sure no other young people in our community"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 243120.0,
      "end_time": 245680.0,
      "text": "end up dead or end up in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 246360.0,
      "end_time": 247936.0,
      "text": "With the grace of God,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247960.0,
      "end_time": 250856.0,
      "text": "the Tariq Khamisa Foundation has been successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250880.0,
      "end_time": 253696.0,
      "text": "We have a safe school model"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253720.0,
      "end_time": 255776.0,
      "text": "which has four different programs."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 255800.0,
      "end_time": 258736.0,
      "text": "The first one is a live assembly with Ples and me."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 258760.0,
      "end_time": 260150.0,
      "text": "We are introduced,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260399.99999999997,
      "end_time": 262960.0,
      "text": "this man&#39;s grandson killed this man&#39;s son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262120.0,
      "end_time": 263456.0,
      "text": "and here they are together."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 263480.0,
      "end_time": 265576.0,
      "text": "We have in-classroom curriculum."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 265600.0,
      "end_time": 269790.0,
      "text": "We have an after school mentoring program, and we create a peace club."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 269920.0,
      "end_time": 271416.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m happy to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 271440.0,
      "end_time": 275336.0,
      "text": "that besides teaching these principles of nonviolence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 275360.0,
      "end_time": 279760.0,
      "text": "we are able to cut suspensions and expulsions by 70 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 280920.0,
      "end_time": 282136.0,
      "text": "which is huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 282160.0,
      "end_time": 283296.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 283320.0,
      "end_time": 284520.0,
      "text": "Which is huge."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 285440.0,
      "end_time": 287856.0,
      "text": "Five years after Tariq died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287880.0,
      "end_time": 290776.0,
      "text": "and for me to complete my journey of forgiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 290800.0,
      "end_time": 293136.0,
      "text": "I went to see the young man who killed my son."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 293160.0,
      "end_time": 294640.0,
      "text": "He was 19 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 295960.0,
      "end_time": 299560.0,
      "text": "And I remember that meeting because we were --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 299800.0,
      "end_time": 301216.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s 37, still in prison --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 301240.0,
      "end_time": 304560.0,
      "text": "but at that first meeting, we locked eyeballs."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 304800.0,
      "end_time": 306895.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m looking in his eyes, he&#39;s looking in my eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 306920.0,
      "end_time": 310576.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m looking in his eyes trying to find a murderer, and I didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 310600.0,
      "end_time": 313336.0,
      "text": "I was able to climb through his eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 313360.0,
      "end_time": 315336.0,
      "text": "and touch his humanity that I got"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 315360.0,
      "end_time": 318976.0,
      "text": "that the spark in him was no different than the spark in me"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 319000.0,
      "end_time": 320520.0,
      "text": "or anybody else here."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 321280.0,
      "end_time": 323575.0,
      "text": "So I wasn&#39;t expecting that. He was remorseful."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 323600.0,
      "end_time": 325696.0,
      "text": "He was articulate. He was well-mannered."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 325720.0,
      "end_time": 329400.0,
      "text": "And I could tell that my hand of forgiveness had changed him."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 331000.0,
      "end_time": 333456.0,
      "text": "So with that, please welcome my brother, Ples."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333480.0,
      "end_time": 336400.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 338920.0,
      "end_time": 343680.0,
      "text": "Ples Felix: Tony is my one and only daughter&#39;s one and only child."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 344360.0,
      "end_time": 346856.0,
      "text": "Tony was born to my daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 346880.0,
      "end_time": 349800.0,
      "text": "who was 15 when she gave birth to Tony."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 350760.0,
      "end_time": 353560.0,
      "text": "Mothering is the toughest job on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 354200.0,
      "end_time": 358336.0,
      "text": "There is no tougher job on the planet than raising another human being"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 358360.0,
      "end_time": 361160.0,
      "text": "and making sure they&#39;re safe, secure"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 361400.0,
      "end_time": 363880.0,
      "text": "and well-positioned to be successful in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 364600.0,
      "end_time": 368800.0,
      "text": "Tony experienced a lot of violence in his life as a young kid."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 369000.0,
      "end_time": 370656.0,
      "text": "He saw one of his favorite cousins"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 370680.0,
      "end_time": 373176.0,
      "text": "be murdered in a hail of automatic weapon fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 373200.0,
      "end_time": 375536.0,
      "text": "and gang involvement in Los Angeles."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 375560.0,
      "end_time": 378400.0,
      "text": "He was very traumatized in so many different ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 379360.0,
      "end_time": 380616.0,
      "text": "Tony came to live with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 380640.0,
      "end_time": 383816.0,
      "text": "I wanted to make sure he had everything a kid needed"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 383840.0,
      "end_time": 385440.0,
      "text": "to be successful."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 387120.0,
      "end_time": 389960.0,
      "text": "But on this particular evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 389120.0,
      "end_time": 390496.0,
      "text": "after years of being with me"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 390520.0,
      "end_time": 393960.0,
      "text": "and struggling mightily to try to be successful"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 393120.0,
      "end_time": 396640.0,
      "text": "and to live up to my expectations of being a successful person,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 397560.0,
      "end_time": 400776.0,
      "text": "on this one particular day, Tony ran away from home that evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400800.0,
      "end_time": 403576.0,
      "text": "he went to be with people he thought were his friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 403600.0,
      "end_time": 405560.0,
      "text": "he was given drugs and alcohol"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 405800.0,
      "end_time": 406335.0,
      "text": "and he took them"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 406360.0,
      "end_time": 409616.0,
      "text": "because he thought they would make him feel carefree."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 409640.0,
      "end_time": 413135.0,
      "text": "But all it did was to make his anxiety go higher"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 413160.0,
      "end_time": 414920.0,
      "text": "and to create a more ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 417320.0,
      "end_time": 420440.0,
      "text": "more deadly thinking on his part."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 421280.0,
      "end_time": 422695.0,
      "text": "He was invited to a robbery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 422720.0,
      "end_time": 424680.0,
      "text": "he was given a 9mm handgun."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 425720.0,
      "end_time": 428336.0,
      "text": "And at the presence of an 18-year-old who commanded him"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 428360.0,
      "end_time": 431496.0,
      "text": "and two 14-year-old boys he thought were his friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 431520.0,
      "end_time": 434736.0,
      "text": "he shot and killed Tariq Khamisa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 434760.0,
      "end_time": 436560.0,
      "text": "this man&#39;s son."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 439840.0,
      "end_time": 442256.0,
      "text": "There are no words, there are no words"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 442280.0,
      "end_time": 446320.0,
      "text": "that can express the loss of a child."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 447240.0,
      "end_time": 449696.0,
      "text": "At my understanding that my grandson was responsible"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 449720.0,
      "end_time": 451416.0,
      "text": "for the murder of this human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 451440.0,
      "end_time": 454656.0,
      "text": "I went to the prayer closet, like I was taught by my old folks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 454680.0,
      "end_time": 456816.0,
      "text": "and began to pray and meditate."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 456840.0,
      "end_time": 459296.0,
      "text": "The one thing that Mr. Khamisa and I have in common,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 459320.0,
      "end_time": 462256.0,
      "text": "and we didn&#39;t know this, besides being wonderful human beings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 462280.0,
      "end_time": 463500.0,
      "text": "is that we both meditate."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 463530.0,
      "end_time": 464679.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 464920.0,
      "end_time": 466376.0,
      "text": "It was very helpful for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 466400.0,
      "end_time": 469895.0,
      "text": "because it offered me an opportunity to seek guidance and clarity"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 469920.0,
      "end_time": 475696.0,
      "text": "about how I wanted to be of support of this man and his family in this loss."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 475720.0,
      "end_time": 477776.0,
      "text": "And sure enough, my prayers were answered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 477800.0,
      "end_time": 480736.0,
      "text": "because I was invited to a meeting at this man&#39;s house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 480760.0,
      "end_time": 483575.0,
      "text": "met his mother, his father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 483600.0,
      "end_time": 486656.0,
      "text": "his wife, his brother, met their family"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 486680.0,
      "end_time": 491896.0,
      "text": "and had a chance to be in the presence of God-spirited people led by this man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 491920.0,
      "end_time": 494960.0,
      "text": "who in the spirit of forgiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 494120.0,
      "end_time": 496640.0,
      "text": "made way, made an opportunity for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 497680.0,
      "end_time": 500656.0,
      "text": "to be of value and to share with him and to share with children"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 500680.0,
      "end_time": 505896.0,
      "text": "the importance of understanding the need to be with a responsible adult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 505920.0,
      "end_time": 508296.0,
      "text": "focus on your anger in a way that&#39;s healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 508320.0,
      "end_time": 509776.0,
      "text": "learn to meditate."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 509800.0,
      "end_time": 512816.0,
      "text": "The programs that we have in the Tariq Khamisa Foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 512840.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515896.00000000006,
      "text": "provide so many tools for the kids to put in their toolkit"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 515919.0,
      "end_time": 518175.0,
      "text": "so they could carry them throughout their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 518200.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521496.00000000006,
      "text": "It&#39;s important that our children understand that loving, caring adults"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 521520.0,
      "end_time": 523550.0,
      "text": "care for them and support them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 523799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 527296.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also important that our children learn to meditate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 527320.0,
      "end_time": 528976.0,
      "text": "learn to be peaceful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 529000.0,
      "end_time": 530456.0,
      "text": "learn to be centered"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 530480.0,
      "end_time": 532775.0,
      "text": "and learn to interact with the other children"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 532799.0,
      "end_time": 534775.0,
      "text": "in a kind, empathetic"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 534799.0,
      "end_time": 536935.0,
      "text": "and wonderfully loving way."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 536960.0,
      "end_time": 538616.0,
      "text": "We need more love in our society"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 538640.0,
      "end_time": 541856.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s why we are here to share the love with children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 541880.0,
      "end_time": 544496.0,
      "text": "because our children will lead the way for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 544520.0,
      "end_time": 547960.0,
      "text": "because all of us will depend on our children."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 547120.0,
      "end_time": 550696.0,
      "text": "As we grow older and retire, they will take over this world for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 550720.0,
      "end_time": 554456.0,
      "text": "so as much love as we teach them, they will give it back to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 554480.0,
      "end_time": 555856.0,
      "text": "Blessings. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 555880.0,
      "end_time": 559880.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 562400.0,
      "end_time": 566960.0,
      "text": "AK: So I was born in Kenya, I was educated in England,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 566120.0,
      "end_time": 568856.0,
      "text": "and my brother here is a Baptist."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 568880.0,
      "end_time": 570840.0,
      "text": "I practice as a Sufi Muslim."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 571480.0,
      "end_time": 572736.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s African American,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 572760.0,
      "end_time": 575656.0,
      "text": "but I always tell him, I&#39;m the African American in the group."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 575680.0,
      "end_time": 577376.0,
      "text": "I was born in Africa. You were not."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 577400.0,
      "end_time": 579696.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 579720.0,
      "end_time": 581896.0,
      "text": "And I naturalized as a citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 581920.0,
      "end_time": 583896.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a first-generation citizen."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 583920.0,
      "end_time": 587695.0,
      "text": "And I felt that, as an American citizen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 587720.0,
      "end_time": 590856.0,
      "text": "I must take my share of the responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 590880.0,
      "end_time": 593320.0,
      "text": "for the murder of my son."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 593840.0,
      "end_time": 597536.0,
      "text": "Why? Because it was fired by an American child."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 597560.0,
      "end_time": 600455.0,
      "text": "You could take the position, he killed my one and only son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 600480.0,
      "end_time": 602720.0,
      "text": "he should be hung from the highest pole."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 603520.0,
      "end_time": 606456.0,
      "text": "How does that improve society?"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 606480.0,
      "end_time": 609880.0,
      "text": "And I know you are probably wondering what happened to that young man."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 610560.0,
      "end_time": 615496.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s still in prison. He just turned 37 on September 22,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 615520.0,
      "end_time": 617415.0,
      "text": "but I have some good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 617440.0,
      "end_time": 620216.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve been trying to get him out for 12 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 620240.0,
      "end_time": 623456.0,
      "text": "He finally will join us a year from now."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 623480.0,
      "end_time": 627120.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 630240.0,
      "end_time": 632976.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m very excited to have him join us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 633000.0,
      "end_time": 635960.0,
      "text": "because I know we&#39;ve saved him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 635120.0,
      "end_time": 638576.0,
      "text": "but he will save tens of thousands of students"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 638600.0,
      "end_time": 641960.0,
      "text": "when he shares his testimony"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 641120.0,
      "end_time": 644496.0,
      "text": "in schools that we are present at on a regular basis."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 644520.0,
      "end_time": 647856.0,
      "text": "When he says to the kids, \"When I was 11, I joined a gang."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 647880.0,
      "end_time": 650776.0,
      "text": "When I was 14, I murdered Mr. Khamisa&#39;s son."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 650800.0,
      "end_time": 653376.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve spent the last umpteen years in prison."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 653400.0,
      "end_time": 656456.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here to tell you: it&#39;s not worth it,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 656480.0,
      "end_time": 659960.0,
      "text": "do you think the kids will listen to that voice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 659120.0,
      "end_time": 661656.0,
      "text": "Yes, because his intonations"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 661680.0,
      "end_time": 664976.0,
      "text": "will be of a person that pulled the trigger."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 665000.0,
      "end_time": 669560.0,
      "text": "And I know that he wants to turn the clock back."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 670480.0,
      "end_time": 672136.0,
      "text": "Of course, that&#39;s not possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 672160.0,
      "end_time": 674736.0,
      "text": "I wish it was. I would have my son back."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 674760.0,
      "end_time": 677400.0,
      "text": "My brother would have his grandson back."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 677920.0,
      "end_time": 681880.0,
      "text": "So I think that demonstrates the power of forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 683640.0,
      "end_time": 685720.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s the big takeaway here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 687400.0,
      "end_time": 690136.0,
      "text": "So I want to end our session with this quote,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 690160.0,
      "end_time": 692856.0,
      "text": "which is the basis of my fourth book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 692880.0,
      "end_time": 694736.0,
      "text": "which incidentally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 694760.0,
      "end_time": 697200.0,
      "text": "the foreword for that book was written by Tony."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 698800.0,
      "end_time": 702736.0,
      "text": "So it goes like this: sustained goodwill creates friendship."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 702760.0,
      "end_time": 704976.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t make friends by bombing them, right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 705000.0,
      "end_time": 706896.0,
      "text": "You make friends by extending goodwill."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 706920.0,
      "end_time": 708336.0,
      "text": "That ought to be obvious."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 708360.0,
      "end_time": 710816.0,
      "text": "So sustained goodwill creates friendship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 710840.0,
      "end_time": 713256.0,
      "text": "sustained friendship creates trust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 713280.0,
      "end_time": 715696.0,
      "text": "sustained trust creates empathy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 715720.0,
      "end_time": 718960.0,
      "text": "sustained empathy creates compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 718120.0,
      "end_time": 720640.0,
      "text": "and sustained compassion creates peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 721200.0,
      "end_time": 722976.0,
      "text": "I call this my peace formula."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 723000.0,
      "end_time": 728976.0,
      "text": "It starts with goodwill, friendship, trust, empathy, compassion and peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 729000.0,
      "end_time": 731736.0,
      "text": "But people ask me, how do you extend goodwill"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 731760.0,
      "end_time": 734360.0,
      "text": "to the person who murdered your child?"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 734800.0,
      "end_time": 737335.0,
      "text": "I tell them, you do that through forgiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 737360.0,
      "end_time": 739496.0,
      "text": "As it&#39;s evident it worked for me."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 739520.0,
      "end_time": 741415.0,
      "text": "It worked for my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 741440.0,
      "end_time": 744960.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s a miracle is it worked for Tony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 744120.0,
      "end_time": 746256.0,
      "text": "it worked for his family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 746280.0,
      "end_time": 749496.0,
      "text": "it can work for you and your family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 749520.0,
      "end_time": 752496.0,
      "text": "for Israel and Palestine, North and South Korea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 752520.0,
      "end_time": 755376.0,
      "text": "for Iraq, Afghanistan, Iran and Syria."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 755400.0,
      "end_time": 758000.0,
      "text": "It can work for the United States of America."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 758680.0,
      "end_time": 761935.0,
      "text": "So let me leave you with this, my sisters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 761960.0,
      "end_time": 763296.0,
      "text": "and a couple of brothers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 763320.0,
      "end_time": 765296.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 765320.0,
      "end_time": 767800.0,
      "text": "that peace is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 768400.0,
      "end_time": 769736.0,
      "text": "How do I know that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 769760.0,
      "end_time": 771616.0,
      "text": "Because I am at peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 771640.0,
      "end_time": 773616.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much. Namaste."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 773640.0,
      "end_time": 776720.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}